<plot>'Teeth' focuses on Ernie, an 80 year old RAF veteran whose wife was killed in a bombing raid during World War II. Discovering years later that she has been 'reincarnated' as the Toothfairy he now steals children's teeth from under their pillows so that she will appear to him instead and the couple can, however briefly, be reunited.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?534040</url></doc>
